The paper deals with the task of training a customized student network using pre-trained deep networks, which is a common problem in the field of machine learning. The paper focuses on the extraction and amalgamation of knowledge from heterogeneous teachers, which is a key aspect of deep learning. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing).
